  {
    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Open a LONG position on Base token\\n\\nLONG Base = betting Base will appreciate vs Quote\\nFlow: Flash loan Quote \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Swap Quote\\xe2\\x86\\x92Base \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Supply Base as collateral \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Borrow Quote \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Repay flash loan\\nResult: Collateral=Base, Debt=Quote\\n\\nArguments:\\n- caller: The user opening the position\\n- flash_amount: Amount of Quote token to flash loan (also repay amount)\\n- initial_margin: Amount of token the user provides as margin\\n- collateral_amount: Amount of Base token to supply as collateral (for supply_collateral request)\\n- collateral_from_base: If true, user provides Base token as margin.\\ncollateral_amount = swap_output + initial_margin\\nborrow_amount = flash_amount (need full amount since margin is different token)\\nIf false, user provides Quote token as margin.\\ncollateral_amount = swap_output only\\nborrow_amount = flash_amount - initial_margin (margin helps repay flash loan)\\n- swap_chain: Custom swap chain for multi-hop swaps. Empty Vec uses default direct swap.",
      "name": "open_long",
      "inputs": [
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "caller",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "flash_amount",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "initial_margin",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "min_swap_output",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "margin_from_quote",
          "type_": "bool"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "swap_chain",
          "type_": {
            "vec": {
              "element_type": {
                "udt": {
                  "name": "SwapHop"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "result": {
            "ok_type": {
              "tuple": {
                "value_types": []
              }
            },
            "error_type": {
              "udt": {
                "name": "EntrypointError"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Open a SHORT position on Base token\\n\\nSHORT Base = betting Base will depreciate vs Quote\\nFlow: Flash loan Base \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Swap Base\\xe2\\x86\\x92Quote \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Supply Quote as collateral \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Borrow Base \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Repay flash loan\\nResult: Collateral=Quote, Debt=Base\\n\\nArguments:\\n- caller: The user opening the position\\n- flash_amount: Amount of Base token to flash loan (also repay amount)\\n- initial_margin: Amount of token the user provides as margin\\n- collateral_amount: Amount of Quote token to supply as collateral (for supply_collateral request)\\n- collateral_from_quote: If true, user provides Quote token as margin.\\ncollateral_amount = swap_output + initial_margin\\nborrow_amount = flash_amount (need full amount since margin is different token)\\nIf false, user provides Base token as margin.\\ncollateral_amount = swap_output only\\nborrow_amount = flash_amount - initial_margin (margin helps repay flash loan)\\n- swap_chain: Custom swap chain for multi-hop swaps. Empty Vec uses default direct swap.",
      "name": "open_short",
      "inputs": [
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "caller",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "flash_amount",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "initial_margin",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "min_swap_output",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "margin_from_quote",
          "type_": "bool"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "swap_chain",
          "type_": {
            "vec": {
              "element_type": {
                "udt": {
                  "name": "SwapHop"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "result": {
            "ok_type": {
              "tuple": {
                "value_types": []
              }
            },
            "error_type": {
              "udt": {
                "name": "EntrypointError"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Reduce or close a LONG position on Base token\\n\\nTo reduce/close long (Collateral=Base, Debt=Quote):\\nFlow: Flash loan Base \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Swap Base\\xe2\\x86\\x92Quote \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Repay Quote debt \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Withdraw Base collateral \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Repay Base flash loan\\n\\nArguments:\\n- caller: The user reducing the position\\n- flash_amount: Amount of Base token to flash loan (will be swapped to Quote)\\n- repay_amount: Amount of Quote debt to repay (expected output from swap)\\n- withdraw_amount: Amount of Base collateral to withdraw (used to repay flash loan)\\n- swap_chain: Custom swap chain for multi-hop swaps. Empty Vec uses default direct swap.",
      "name": "close_long",
      "inputs": [
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "caller",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "flash_amount",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "repay_amount",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "withdraw_amount",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "swap_chain",
          "type_": {
            "vec": {
              "element_type": {
                "udt": {
                  "name": "SwapHop"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "result": {
            "ok_type": {
              "tuple": {
                "value_types": []
              }
            },
            "error_type": {
              "udt": {
                "name": "EntrypointError"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
